## Import



Using `pulumi import`, import AWS Chime SDK Voice Global Settings using the `id` (AWS account ID). For example:

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:chime/sdkvoiceGlobalSettings:SdkvoiceGlobalSettings example 123456789012
```
